---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Tile & Backsplash
description: A full Daltile showroom plus natural stone and glass mosaics — set by the same crew that installs your counters.
permalink: /tile/
---

<div class="page-head page-head--split">
  <div>
    <span class="kicker">Tile &amp; Backsplash</span>
    <h1>The finishing layer.</h1>
  </div>
  <p class="lede lede--sm" style="max-width:40ch">A full Daltile showroom plus natural stone and glass mosaics — set by the same crew that installs your counters.</p>
</div>

<div class="grid grid--3" style="padding:8px var(--pad-x) 56px; gap:28px 20px">
  {% for c in tile %}
    <div class="card">
      {% if c.image %}
        <div class="photo"><img src="{{ c.image }}" alt="{{ c.alt }}" loading="lazy"></div>
      {% else %}
        {% set c1 = c.bg.split(',') | first %}
        {% set c2 = c.bg.split(',') | last %}
        <div class="ph" style="background:repeating-linear-gradient(45deg, {{ c1 }}, {{ c1 }} 10px, {{ c2 }} 10px, {{ c2 }} 20px)">
          <span>{{ c.name | lower }} sample</span>
        </div>
      {% endif %}
      <span class="card__title card__title--lg">{{ c.name }}</span>
      <span class="card__meta" style="font-size:13px">{{ c.desc }}</span>
    </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>

<p style="margin:0;padding:0 var(--pad-x) 40px;font:400 12px var(--sans);color:var(--faint)">Room scenes courtesy of Daltile. WGMT is an authorized Daltile dealer.</p>

{% set cta = { text: "Bringing a backsplash idea? We’ll match it to your stone.", button: "Plan a Showroom Visit" } %}
{% include "partials/cross-cta.njk" %}
